msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ansible-integration.adoc:6
msgid "discovery of playbooks"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ansible-integration.adoc:7
msgid "execution of playbooks"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ansible-integration.adoc:8
msgid "For more information:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ansible-integration.adoc:9
msgid ""
"The inventory is a sorted list of managed Ansible nodes.  For more "
"information about organizing an inventory, see https://docs.ansible.com/"
"ansible/latest/inventory_guide/intro_inventory.html."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ansible-integration.adoc:10
msgid ""
"Playbooks are a way to describe how the inventory is to be managed.  For "
"more information about playbooks, see https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/"
