msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/ansible-integration.adoc:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Requirements and Basic Configuration"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ansible-integration.adoc:12
msgid ""
"To use Ansible features, you need to register the already existing Ansible "
"Control Node as a Salt client to the {productname} Server.  In the {webui}, "
"on the menu:System Details[Properties] page of the registered system, you "
"must enable the ``Ansible Control Node`` system type of the [guimenu]``Add-"
"on System Types`` list."
