#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:53
msgid ""
"Before you begin, ensure that the client to be scanned has Python and XML-"
"RPC libraries installed."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:54
msgid ""
"Choose an existing script or create a script for scheduling a system scan "
"through ``system.scap.scheduleXccdfScan``.  For example:"
