#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/reports.adoc:2
msgid ""
"{productname} allows the user to produce a variety of reports.  These "
"reports can be helpful for taking inventory of your subscribed systems, "
"users, and organizations.  Using reports is often simpler than gathering "
"information manually from the {productname} {webui}, especially if you have "
"many systems under management."
