"this case, bugs can show up even after updating to a version that resolves "
"the bug, because the cache is still using invalid entries.  If you upgrade "
"to a new version of ISS, but are still experiencing problems, clear all the "
"caches to ensure you no longer have old entries creating a problem."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-iss.adoc:3
